---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title={`关于我 | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
			description="关于独孤伶俜的博客背景与个人介绍"
		/>
	</head>
	<body
		class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 transition-colors duration-300"
	>
		<Header />

		<main
			class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-10 font-body relative overflow-hidden min-h-[max(calc(100vh-200px),600px)]"
		>
			<div
				class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-16 mb-24 mt-12 relative z-10 pl-4 md:pl-10 text-left w-full"
			>
				<!-- Red Vertical Stroke Accent -->
				<div
					class="absolute left-0 top-2 bottom-4 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-[#bc152d] via-[#bc152d]/50 to-transparent shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(188,21,45,0.4)] text-left"
				>
				</div>

				<!-- Text Column -->
				<div class="w-full lg:max-w-2xl">
					<span
						class="text-[#bc152d] font-body text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-8 block"
						>About the Author</span
					>

					<h1
						class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-widest mb-12 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 leading-tight flex flex-wrap items-center"
					>
						逻辑 · 平衡 · 电波<span
							class="animate-blink ml-1 font-mono text-[#bc152d]"
							>_</span
						>
					</h1>

					<!-- Content Block -->
					<div
						class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none font-body text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 tracking-wider relative z-20 transition-colors"
					>
						<h2
							class="font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 mt-0 mb-4 font-bold border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-2"
						>
							[ 身份校验 / Identity ]
						</h2>
						<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400">
							你好，我是独孤伶俜。
						</p>
						<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400">
							毕业于天津理工大学。早年是个标准的软件狗，打过蓝桥杯（已退役）和
							<del>ACM</del>。
						</p>
						<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400">
							目前我的主业是一名核算会计。在此之前，曾在某市调公司工作，主要在
							Confirmit 平台上使用 JScript
							语言编写问卷逻辑，偶尔也用 JavaScript
							写写网页端逻辑；期间还曾使用 Java
							做过一些四方支付程序的二次开发。
						</p>
						<p class="mb-10 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400">
							现在写代码更多是出于纯粹的爱好，目前主要使用 Go
							语言在造一些业余项目的轮子。此外，我也是一名业余无线电爱好者，目前主要活跃于
							<a
								href="https://bg5esn.com/docs/"
								target="_blank"
								class="text-[#bc152d] hover:text-[#ffb3b1] transition-colors no-underline"
								>FMO</a
							> 网络。我的呼号是 <strong>BG9JYT</strong
							>，期待在频段里与您建立通联。
						</p>

						<h2
							class="font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 mt-12 mb-4 font-bold border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-2"
						>
							[ 运行状态 / Status ]
						</h2>
						<ul
							class="list-none pl-0 mb-10 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-3"
						>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>-</span
								><span>备考 2026 年中级会计师考试。</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>-</span
								><span>备考 2026 年税务师考试。</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>-</span
								><span style="text-decoration: line-through"
									>备考业余无线电操作证 B 证。</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>-</span
								><span>寻找没有版权争议的雪山视频 BGM。</span>
							</li>
						</ul>

						<h2
							class="font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 mt-12 mb-4 font-bold border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-2"
						>
							[ 研发归档 / Projects ]
						</h2>
						<p
							class="mb-4 font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
						>
							近期在写<span
								class="animate-pulse ml-0.5 opacity-60 font-mono text-[#bc152d]"
								>_</span
							>
						</p>
						<ul
							class="list-none pl-0 mb-8 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-3"
						>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>&gt;</span
								><span
									><strong>fmoqc / fmomap</strong>：基于 Go
									语言的 FMO 节点地图可视化与系统开发。</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>&gt;</span
								><span
									><strong>eQSL 系统</strong
									>：现代化的业余无线电电子卡片（eQSL）生成与管理系统。</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>&gt;</span
								><span
									><strong>四方支付系统</strong
									>：探索“小而美”架构的独立支付网关系统。</span
								>
							</li>
						</ul>

						<p
							class="mb-4 font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 mt-8"
						>
							早年造的轮子<span
								class="animate-pulse ml-0.5 opacity-60 font-mono text-[#bc152d]"
								>_</span
							>
						</p>
						<ul
							class="list-none pl-0 mb-10 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-3"
						>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>&gt;</span
								><span
									><strong>Music163API</strong
									>：高品质、简单易用的网易云音乐 API 服务。</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>&gt;</span
								><span
									><strong>一言 (hitokoto) API</strong
									>：支持自建私有库的句子接口。</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] font-mono mr-3"
									>&gt;</span
								><span
									><strong>Typecho 模板</strong
									>：一套以前自用的博客皮肤。</span
								>
							</li>
						</ul>

						<h2
							class="font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 mt-12 mb-4 font-bold border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-2"
						>
							[ 通讯链路 / Contact ]
						</h2>
						<p class="mb-6 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400">
							除单独说明外，本站文章默认采用 <a
								href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/deed.zh"
								target="_blank"
								class="text-[#bc152d] hover:text-[#ffb3b1] transition-colors no-underline"
								>知识共享署名-相同方式共享 4.0 国际许可协议</a
							> 进行许可。如果你对代码、无线电有兴趣，或者想交流一下考证心得，可以通过以下方式找到我：
						</p>
						<ul
							class="list-none pl-0 mb-10 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-400 space-y-3 font-mono text-sm tracking-wide"
						>
							<li class="flex items-center">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] mr-3">-</span
								><strong
									class="w-24 font-normal text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
									>Email:</strong
								><a
									href="mailto:admin@icyuyan.net"
									class="hover:text-[#bc152d] dark:hover:text-[#ffb3b1] transition-colors no-underline"
									>admin@icyuyan.net</a
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] mr-3">-</span
								><strong
									class="w-24 font-normal text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
									>Github:</strong
								><a
									href="https://github.com/yeyuxingchen"
									target="_blank"
									class="hover:text-[#bc152d] dark:hover:text-[#ffb3b1] transition-colors no-underline"
									>@独孤伶俜</a
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] mr-3">-</span
								><strong
									class="w-24 font-normal text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
									>Weibo:</strong
								><span
									class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
									>@独孤伶俜233</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] mr-3">-</span
								><strong
									class="w-24 font-normal text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
									>Twitter:</strong
								><a
									href="https://twitter.com/dugulingping"
									target="_blank"
									class="hover:text-[#bc152d] dark:hover:text-[#ffb3b1] transition-colors no-underline"
									>@dugulingping</a
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] mr-3">-</span
								><strong
									class="w-24 font-normal text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
									>BiliBili:</strong
								><a
									href="http://space.bilibili.com/65041587"
									target="_blank"
									class="hover:text-[#bc152d] dark:hover:text-[#ffb3b1] transition-colors no-underline"
									>@独孤伶俜_</a
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center">
								<span class="text-[#bc152d] mr-3">-</span
								><strong
									class="w-24 font-normal text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
									>NetEase:</strong
								><a
									href="http://music.163.com/#/user/home?id=137630579"
									target="_blank"
									class="hover:text-[#bc152d] dark:hover:text-[#ffb3b1] transition-colors no-underline"
									>@独孤伶俜</a
								>
							</li>
						</ul>

						<!-- <div class="mt-12 pt-0 w-full flex items-center">
							<a href="mailto:admin@icyuyan.net" class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto justify-center items-center gap-3 px-6 py-2.5 bg-transparent text-neutral-900 dark:text-white font-medium rounded-none border border-neutral-900 dark:border-white hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity duration-300 no-underline uppercase tracking-widest text-sm group">
								<svg class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.012 8.012 0 0 0 16 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"></path></svg>
								[ 建立通联 / ESTABLISH QSO ]
							</a>
						</div> -->
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
